{"tid":232442,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"學資處問題 急 求解","createTime":"2017-05-06T17:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T12:56:17.000Z","uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7f6cbd0e840b7f20f851dd129e46d3444819676","tid":232442,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:44:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我12月quit左u<br />\n但唔記得通知學資處<br />\n之前借左y1學費42000<br />\n我預之後會入番u<br />\n之後會再申請學生資助<br />\n<br />\n咁到底我洗唔洗還錢？<br />\n（我見佢有得拖延，但我又未知我入番乜u，填唔到個個表住）<br />\n<br />\n遲左通知後果係點？會唔會影響我之後嘅申請？<br />\n<br />\n依家還會唔會迫我一次過還？<br />\n（我好窮）<br />\n<br />\n祝解答嘅巴絲一世平安健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d2cab6d2cb01e6b5cf2514b4fe7b2e293ba3f3","tid":232442,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf0fba347967f2aa0230bf08742572be6302659","tid":232442,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:45:24.000Z","msg":"無意唔還錢<br />\n只係想知遲左通知有無後果"},{"pid":"5c18433a0695dd3bc6ad304c9b2b7502f48c894b","tid":232442,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:45:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3183166e94d802c0a319bf84bf5333bdc614856e","tid":232442,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:46:33.000Z","msg":"祝巴絲中六合彩 早日買樓 有好男女朋友<img src=\"/assets/